(160, 3, 'Lemon Chicken Stir-Fry', 2, 'en', 'United States', 'Who knew that lemon works so well in a stir-fry? A delicious twist.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Juice the lemon in a small bowl; add broth, soy sauce, and cornstarch. Grate 0.5 teaspoon lemon zest for the stir-fry.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the carrots, scallions, and mushroom into the desired shape. Slice the chicken in thin dices. &nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cook the chicken in a pan until done, about 4-5 minutes. If you use oil or non-stick spray, be aware that nutritional value changes as I cook mine in water. Take out the chicken and place it on a plate.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>In the same pan, cook mushrooms and carrots until they soften, about 4 minutes. Add scallion, garlic, lemon zest and snow peas. Cook for about a minute.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 5</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the sauce and let cook until thickened, about 2-3 minutes. Add the chicken and cook until it is covered in sauce and heated through. This shouldn&rsquo;t take more than a minute or two.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Serve with&nbsp;rice or<a href=\"http://cicolife.net/view_recipe.php?recipe_id=125&amp;l=en\">&nbsp;zucchini noodles</a>! Top with crushed red pepper.&nbsp;Feel free to omit and vegetables you do not like. Other substitutes for vegetables can be green beans, zucchini, or bell peppers.&nbsp;</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2018', '160.jpeg', '160-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-11-20', '17:44:09', 2, 0, 0, '', 1400, '161.97.136.234\n144.76.120.197\n2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n95.91.110.121\n2607:5300:60:3880::1\n185.191.171.10\n185.191.171.39', 0, '2605:e000:614d:6100:3de7:5eec:3d89:697d', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '194831295da7dd3f50e005f4ef6636e48d56a746', '2020-12-27 06:37:56', 0),
(162, 3, 'Orange Infused Green Beans and Red Peppers', 6, 'en', 'United States', 'I love green beans, they are so versatile and low in calories. This recipe is a great side with sweetness from the orange and heat from crushed red peppers.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Preheat oven to 400 F.&nbsp; Remove the seeds from the bell pepper. Chop the bell pepper into thin strips and trim the green beans.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grate the orange using a flat grater so you get long strips.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix the green beans, orange peel, salt, and non-stick spray in a bowl.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>Spread the vegetables on a parchment paper covered baking sheet and put in the oven. Let cook for about 15 minutes, turning once.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Serve with crushed red peppers.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/3/2019', '162.jpeg', '162-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-11-25', '20:04:04', 0, 0, 0, '', 1283, '114.119.137.125\n167.114.116.38\n192.99.15.199\n2a01:4f8:190:4324::2\n167.114.159.183\n2607:5300:120:5ca::1\n2a01:4f8:162:14e::2', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:c40f:2a08:f1c0:3b36', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', 'dbd657179da2a6cf8f84411e9e5f2cd020666dfb', '2020-12-26 10:55:56', 0),
(166, 3, 'Beef and Broccoli Stir-fry', 2, 'en', 'United States', 'Such a simple but tasty recipe. It has a lot of broccoli that helps you keep full throughout the day. Eat one serving tonight and have the other for lunch tomorrow.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mince the garlic and ginger. Chop broccoli and scallions. Slice beef into thin strips.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>In a small glass bowl add water and cornstarch and mix well. Add&nbsp;soy sauce, sugar substitute, ginger, and red pepper. Mix.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Brown the beef in a pan until done, 3-6 minutes. Set aside.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add garlic&nbsp;and green onions to the pan, let cook for two minutes before adding broccoli. Cook another 5 minutes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 5</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stir the sauce to make sure the cornstarch&nbsp;is mixed. Add it to the pan with the broccoli, and cook until it thickens about 3 minutes. Add beef and cook until its heated through for another 2-3 minutes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Serve with rice, steamed vegetables, or a green salad. Add salt and pepper to taste.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2018', '166.jpeg', '166-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-12-03', '17:36:05', 2, 0, 0, '', 1372, '2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n2a01:4f8:161:8046::2\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n167.114.158.241\n2a01:4f8:191:2094::2\n62.138.2.243\n2a01:4f8:162:8b::2\n167.114.116.38\n2607:5300:60:3b2f::1\n2607:5300:60:37e2::1', 0, '2605:e000:614d:6100:acd0:95a4:7334:52fd', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '67021c328dedbbf2a8a3d6eb28959ded25189384', '2020-12-25 15:33:43', 0),
(168, 3, 'Cauliflower soup', 2, 'en', 'United States', 'Enjoy with freshly toasted bread.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Dice the onion, garlic,&nbsp;and cauliflower.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Brown the onion in a pot for about 3 minutes then add garlic and let cook another minute. I brown mine in a tablespoon chicken stock. If you use oil remember to adjust the overall calorie content to reflect upon that.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the chicken stock and cauliflower. Bring to a boil and cover the pot. Let simmer for about 20-25 minutes, until the cauliflower is tender.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>Use an immersion blender or heat-safe blender to puree the soup and serve.&nbsp; Add salt and pepper to taste.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2018', '168.jpeg', '168-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-12-14', '20:56:50', 0, 0, 0, '', 1763, '2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n2a01:4f8:161:8046::2\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n185.191.171.23\n167.114.158.241\n114.119.156.144\n2a01:4f8:191:2094::2\n62.138.2.243', 0, '81.166.21.244', '', 'eec937cdbc1c66e565d8f5cd603296cad6eaec21', '2020-12-25 15:34:08', 0),
(169, 3, 'Greek yogurt bark', 4, 'en', 'United States', '23 grams protein! Great for breakfast or as a snack.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;In a bowl mix yogurt, vanilla, and stevia.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cover a 9x9 inch freezer-safe dish with parchment paper. Spread the yogurt mix on top of the parchment paper. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Top with diced strawberry and grated chocolate.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>Freeze for at least 3 hours. Let melt 10 minutes before breaking into pieces and serve.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"background-color: rgba(246, 213, 217, 0.01);\">Get creative, switch out strawberries with goji berries or blueberries! Top with coconut flakes instead of chocolate, or perhaps both!&nbsp;<br /></span></p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2019', '169.jpeg', '169-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-12-14', '21:28:43', 0, 0, 0, '', 1759, '114.119.138.25\n185.191.171.35\n2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n2a01:4f8:161:8046::2\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n167.114.158.241\n185.191.171.17\n2a01:4f8:191:2094::2\n2a01:4f8:162:8b::2\n62.138.2.243\n167.114.116.38', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:1c74:a2cb:9048:e51d', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', 'cc19461a45c5a9fc76fd3e12b37e7e29596efddd', '2020-12-27 08:31:52', 0),
(171, 3, 'Skinny Maple Oatmeal', 1, 'en', 'United States', 'I love Better Oats Oatmeal Maple &amp; Brown Sugar but it never fills me up. So I&#039;ve created multiple maple oatmeals to create one similar in flavor but more filling :-)', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine oats, water, cinnamon, maple extract, and cinnamon in a pot or a large microwave-safe dish. <br />Microwave for 4-5 minutes, let rest until it cools.<br />Stove, let simmer for 10-15 minutes, let stand until it cools.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once cooled leave in the fridge for 6+ hours or overnight.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy it hot or cold: re-heat it in the microwave for one-two minutes or if you enjoy a pudding-like consistency enjoy it cold. Sweeten with your favorite sweetener.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Serve with your favorite toppings such as brown sugar, chopped pecans, banana,&nbsp; fresh berries like strawberries or raspberries.<br /><br /><span data-offset-key=\"5gmsc-0-0\"><strong>I recommend adding a dash salt in your oatmeal. Salt enhances the flavor by bringing out the sweetness and nuttiness from rolled oats.<br /><br /></strong><br />I make my oatmeal using double the amount of water and cook time known as the&nbsp;voluminous oatmeal trick. <a href=\"view_recipe.php?recipe_id=13&amp;l=en\">See this recipe for reference.</a> If you prefer your oats the regular way just follow the directions on how to cook the oats according to the package and add the other ingredients in order. <br /></span></p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/1/3/2019', '171.jpg', '171-thumb.jpg', '', '2018-12-14', '22:14:18', 0, 0, 0, '', 1292, '161.97.136.234\n2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n95.91.110.121\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.158.241\n37.57.218.243\n2a01:4f8:191:2094::2', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:7412:356f:8bde:bf70', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '2a62e5510bcadac7d6a18d858141b852c2da1295', '2020-12-27 06:38:01', 0),
(172, 16, 'Kebab av karbonadedeig', 2, 'no', '', 'Hvem hadde trudd at kebab kunne v&aelig;re s&aring; sunt!', '<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Bland krydder og karbonadedeig sammen i en bolle. Del deigen i 4 like deler og form hver til en kebab. Sett et grillspyd i hver kebab og bÃ¸rst de med olje.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Stekes pÃ¥ en grillpanne for best smak. Kan ogsÃ¥ stekes i vanlig panne eller stekeovn med grill funksjon. Stekes i ca 5-8 minutter, eller til hver kebab er gjennomstekt.</p>\r\n<p>Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Server medÂ agurksalat og mynteyogurt. </p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/2/2018', '172.jpeg', '172_thumb_278x184.png', '', '2018-12-16', '21:11:03', 6, 0, 0, '0', 1387, '127.0.0.1\n185.191.171.45\n161.97.136.234\n2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n95.91.110.121\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.158.241\n192.99.13.75\n2a01:4f8:191:2094::2\n62.138.2.243', 0, '81.166.21.244', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', 'e0424c95da85d3fa86b3895a334fda4b124b7220', '2020-12-31 19:45:05', 0),
(173, 16, 'Mynteyogurt', 6, 'no', '', 'Kan serveres til kebab, salat, karrimiddager, i pitabr&oslash;d eller som dip til gr&oslash;nnsaker,.', '<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Finkutt mynte</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Bland sammen yogurt, mynte, salt og eddik. </p>\r\n<p>Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Sett gjerne i kjÃ¸leskapet 20 minutter fÃ¸r servering. </p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/2/2018', '173.jpeg', '173-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-12-16', '21:39:08', 24, 0, 0, '0', 824, '2a01:4f8:210:200b::2\n2a01:4f8:192:8108::2\n2a01:4f8:200:6406::2\n204.12.220.106\n2a01:4f8:140:2155::2\n2a01:e0a:2c2:8e80:65ee:5755:298f:5af5\n2001:41d0:1:e950::1\n2a01:4f8:190:7382::2', 0, '81.166.21.244', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '6f21f7463a7e78585ba36c0830b32174e6365adc', '2020-03-04 14:55:57', 0),
(174, 16, 'Agurk og Mynte salat', 6, 'no', '', 'Deilig og oppfriskende salat!', '<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Kutt agurken i tynne skiver, del den gjerne pÃ¥ siden slik at den blir kuttet i halvmÃ¥ner.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Kutt rÃ¸dlÃ¸k i tynne skiver.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 3</p>\r\n<p>Finkutt mynte. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 4</p>\r\n<p>Bland sammen eddik, salt, pepper, mynte i en liten skÃ¥l.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 5</p>\r\n<p>Bland sÃ¥ alt sammen og server.Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Kan stÃ¥ i kjÃ¸leskapet et par timer ogsÃ¥.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/2/2018', '174.jpeg', '174_thumb_278x184.png', '', '2018-12-16', '22:24:20', 6, 0, 0, '0', 1191, '2a01:4f8:191:2094::2\n62.138.2.243\n173.212.247.190\n2607:5300:60:3b2f::1\n192.99.15.199\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n2a01:4f8:190:4449::2\n185.191.171.19', 0, '81.166.21.244', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '650de32b3a2db5b106966ab4d70fd215cd36a165', '2020-12-22 10:10:39', 0),
(175, 16, 'Sky Br&oslash;d', 6, 'no', '', 'Endelig en m&aring;te &aring; nyte br&oslash;dmat uten karbohydrater! Legg gjerne til forskjellige krydder som oregano, basilikum eller r&oslash;d pepperflak til eggeplommene.', '<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Forvarm ovnen til 150 Â° C og dekk to bakeplater med bakepapir.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Separer eggehvitene i en bolle og eggeplommer i en annen. For best resultat, bruk en glass skÃ¥l for eggehvitene.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 3</p>\r\n<p>Pisk eggehvitene til stive topper danner, vÃ¦r tÃ¥lmodig da dette tar tid. Legg Xanthan Gum mot slutten. Hvis du ikke har Xanthan Gum kan du bruke salt, men resultatet blir ikke like bra.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 4</p>\r\n<p>Tilsett yoghurt (og krydder hvis du Ã¸nsker) i eggeplommer og rÃ¸r sammen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 5</p>\r\n<p>Kombiner eggeplommene og eggehvitene forsiktig. Ikke bruk en elektrisk mikser, rÃ¸r forsiktig med en slikkepinne til alt er kombinert.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 6</p>\r\n<p>Plasser seks skjer av blandingen pÃ¥ hver bakeplate (omtrent en spiseskje hver).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 7</p>\r\n<p>Spre blandingen ut i sirkler med en slikkepinne eller spiseskje til ca. 0.5 cm tykk.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 8Bak i 30 minutter eller til de er gyldene. Tillat de Ã¥ avkjÃ¸le i en time fÃ¸r servering.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Server med ditt favorittpÃ¥legg eller som hamburgerbrÃ¸d.Â </p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/2/2018', '175.jpeg', '175_thumb_278x184.png', '', '2018-12-16', '22:44:37', 0, 0, 0, '0', 1426, '127.0.0.1\n161.97.136.234\n192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n95.91.110.121\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2', 0, '81.166.21.244', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '74345be9d5827a921e2a36b9e66dcf2c80b5fe21', '2020-12-27 18:51:07', 0),
(176, 16, 'Sliders med grillet ananas.', 2, 'no', '', 'Stekt ananas gir slidersen en r&oslash;yket s&oslash;thet mens den raske coleslawen s&oslash;rger for en pikant smak. Kaloriene inkluderer ikke br&oslash;d.', '<p>KetchupÂ </p>\r\n<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Skvis ut juicen av sitron til du fÃ¥r en spiseskje saft. Bland sÃ¥ sammen, sitron, epleeddik og ketchup. Sett til sides</p>\r\n<p>Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Coleslaw</p>\r\n<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Riv eller kutt opp rÃ¸dkÃ¥l, Kutt opp all vÃ¥rlÃ¸ken, sett 50 gram vÃ¥rlÃ¸k til sides.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Skvis ut juicen av en sitron til to spiseskjeer saft.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 3</p>\r\n<p>Bland sammen sitronsaften, epleeddik, salt og pepper i en liten skÃ¥l.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 4</p>\r\n<p>Bland sÃ¥ sammen rÃ¸dkÃ¥l, 50 gram vÃ¥rlÃ¸k og sitron dressingen.</p>\r\n<p>Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Sliders</p>\r\n<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Bland karbonadedeig, 50 gram oppkuttet vÃ¥rlÃ¸k fra tidligere, salt og pepper.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Form til 16 smÃ¥ burgere.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 3</p>\r\n<p>Stek hver burger over middels-hÃ¸y varme i 2-3 minutter fÃ¸r du snur den og steker til den er gjennomstekt, ca 1-2 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 4</p>\r\n<p>Sett ferdigstekte sliders pÃ¥ et fat.</p>\r\n<p>Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Ananas</p>\r\n<ul><li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Kutt opp ananas i 16 tynne ringer eller del til firkanter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Stek i ca 1-2 minutter i samme panne pÃ¥ den ene siden.</p>\r\n<p>Â </p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><p>Sett sÃ¥ sammen hver sliders med slidersbrÃ¸d, bÃ¸rst pÃ¥ ketchup pÃ¥ undersiden, ha en burger oppÃ¥, sÃ¥ en ananas ring og til slutt coleslaw pÃ¥ toppen. Bon AppÃ©tit!</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/2/2018', '176.jpeg', '176-thumb.jpeg', '', '2018-12-16', '23:40:48', 0, 0, 0, '0', 1058, '192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:62d1::2\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2