(300, 3, 'Protein Waffles', 4, 'en', 'United States', 'Delicious and easy way to hit those macro goals!', '<ul style=\"color: #626262;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\">Step 1</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Whip one of the egg whites (33 gram) until stiff peaks forms and set aside.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Add all dry ingredients to a bowl and all wet ingredients to another. Mix each separately.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\">Step 2</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">In the bowl with dry ingredients make a hole in the middle of the flour mix and pour the liquid in. Carefully combine the ingredients, do not over mix just combine until there is no longer any dry flour left. Fold in the egg white until mixed.&nbsp;&nbsp;Let stand 5 minutes so the gluten develops and the batter gets thicker.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\">Step 3</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Cook according to your waffle makers directions. Let waffles rest on a cooling rack.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: #626262;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">I make 9 four inch waffles. Depending on your waffle maker you might have to use non-stick spray. Calculate that into your total nutrition value.</span></p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/4/3/2019', '300.jpg', '300-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-05-16', '06:58:38', 0, 0, 0, '', 990, '192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:120:13af::2\n185.191.171.8\n185.191.171.36\n185.191.171.35\n185.191.171.1\n185.191.171.23\n185.191.171.19\n185.191.171.3', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:8874:f0b7:5e89:5801', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '4500228b6895866ae5102022f53475d770185cc8', '2020-12-14 03:37:46', 0),
(301, 3, 'Spicy Cold Shrimp', 2, 'en', 'United States', 'A great marinade for pre-cooked shrimp.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix all ingredients except shrimp. Pour over shrimp and let marinate in the fridge for 30+ minutes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Serve in a salad, on lettuce leaves, with pasta, or on skewers.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2019', '301.jpg', '301-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-05-16', '07:05:49', 0, 0, 0, '', 622, '185.191.171.2\n185.191.171.41\n185.191.171.10\n185.191.171.21\n185.191.171.1\n185.191.171.23\n192.99.15.199', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:8874:f0b7:5e89:5801', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '8634669f4d93b7e2318bd458e2ee5f6b5091de09', '2020-12-25 10:53:10', 0),
(302, 3, 'Pasta &amp; Chicken Sauce in Slow Cooker', 2, 'en', 'United States', 'Hearty and healthy tomato-based sauce.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop onion, bell pepper, and mushroom.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix all the ingredients in a two-quart slow cooker. Cook on high for 3-4 hours or on low for 7-8 hours.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Serve with pasta or <a href=\"view_recipe.php?recipe_id=125\">zoodles</a> topped with freshly chopped basil or parsley.&nbsp;</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2019', '302.jpg', '302-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-05-17', '01:18:55', 22, 0, 0, '', 1017, '167.114.64.97\n185.191.171.25\n192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n185.191.171.35\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.158.241\n37.57.218.243', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:e0ac:429d:1aa1:dad6', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', 'fdf507a69a7898e861d08b96a02cd25b51e61e83', '2020-12-27 04:51:32', 0),
(303, 3, 'Pumpkin Mousse, Protein Edition', 5, 'en', 'United States', 'Delicious and so easy!', '<ul style=\"color: #626262;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\">Step 1</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bloom your gelatin in a little cold water, about one-two tablespoons. In a separate bowl heat enough water to mix the gelatin in. I do 2-3 tablespoons water and microwave it for 40-50 second. Whisk gelatin and water until dissolved, let it cool until it reaches room temperature.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\">Step 2</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Add greek yogurt, sugar substitute to taste, pumpkin puree, and gelatin into a mixing bowl. Mix well with an electric mixer, for about for 2-4 minutes. You want to whip as much air as possible into the mousse.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\">Step 3</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pour into a 2-cup sized container and let cool in the fridge for 1-2 hours.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: #626262;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Stays well in the fridge for up to 36 hours.<br /><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #626262;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Blooming helps completely dissolve the gelatin.&nbsp;</span></p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/5/3/2019', '303.jpg', '303-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-05-17', '01:25:13', 0, 0, 0, '', 1104, '167.114.64.97\n114.119.138.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.158.241', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:e0ac:429d:1aa1:dad6', '', '62c2f131e0a29abb04a69669d2d2cc0554b24794', '2020-12-27 04:55:20', 0),
(304, 3, 'Troll-Cream', 5, 'en', 'United States', 'A classic Norwegian dessert usually made with Lingonberry.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Puree the berries in a small food processor or by hand using a fork.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Whip the egg white until stiff white peaks forms. Add berries and sugar and continue to whip for 4-5 more minutes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Can be eaten as it is, set cold for 4 hours or frozen for up to 4 hours. When you freeze it the texture becomes more crunchy like.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use pasteurized and safe to eat cartons of raw egg whites.<br /><br />You can use other berries such as blueberries, blackberries, or raspberries.&nbsp;</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/5/3/2019', '304.jpg', '304-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-05-17', '01:32:55', 23, 0, 0, '', 1679, '167.114.64.97\n192.99.9.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n185.191.171.25', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:e0ac:429d:1aa1:dad6', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '6da6563d21d70a3ee61a29625ac637e02dcafa2b', '2020-12-27 04:57:46', 0),
(305, 3, 'Zesty Orange Chicken', 2, 'en', 'United States', 'Use a fresh orange for best flavor', '<ul style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 30px; color: #000000; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\"><strong>Step 1</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\">Chop vegetables and chicken into bite-size pieces. I like to do mine into thin strips or squares.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\"><strong>Step 2</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\">Zest orange and mix sauce ingredients into a small bowl set aside.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\"><strong>Step 3</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\">Coat chicken in cornstarch. Pan fry over medium-high heat until it is done, about 5 minutes. Set aside on a plate.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\"><strong>Step 4</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\">Add all vegetables except scallions and cook until crunchy, 4 minutes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\"><strong>Step 5</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.6; color: #000000;\">Add chicken, scallions and sauce. Cook, until heated throughout and the sauce has thickened for about 3 minutes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff;\">Serve with rice and steamed veggies. Top with red pepper flakes.&nbsp; Feel free to add other vegetables such as snow peas or green beans.&nbsp;</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/3/2019', '305.jpg', '305-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-05-18', '01:31:07', 2, 0, 0, '', 1184, '167.114.64.97\n192.99.9.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n185.191.171.42\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n185.191.171.40\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n114.119.129.199\n167.114.158.241', 0, '2605:e000:6140:f100:b494:4a3e:b492:17ea', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', '047293a4f00ce0371d8e0071b10ae62204810fba', '2020-12-27 05:00:39', 0),
(306, 1, 'Torsk i form med gr&oslash;nnsaker', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Torsk grillet i en form sammen med gr&oslash;nnsaker er noe av det sunneteste man f&aring;r. Server med fullkornpasta og du har en veldig god middag.', '<p>Denne retten har et veldig lavt innhold av fett og karbohydrater. &Oslash;nsker du &aring; kutte mer p&aring; kalorier kan du redusere mengden pasta.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Sett p&aring; ovnen p&aring; 200 grader.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>Legg torskefilet i en form.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>Legg gr&oslash;nnsakene rundt torskefileten. Hvis du ikke liker at det kommer fiskesmak p&aring; gr&oslash;nnsakene kan du legge dem i en annen form, eventuelt skille fisk og gr&oslash;nnsaker ved aleminiumsfolie.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>Sett formen i ovnen. Fisken og gr&oslash;nnsakene skal steke i 30 minutter.<br /><br /></li>\r\n<li>N&aring;r det er g&aring;tt 10 minutter setter du p&aring; en kjele med vann. N&aring;r denne koker har du i pasta. Pastaen skal koke i 7 minutter.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Serveres rykende varmt med god samvittighet!</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '306.jpg', '306-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-11', '15:30:15', 0, 0, 0, '', 179, '167.114.64.97\n192.99.9.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.159.99', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '6f8d18ae1b441f68c8df3904060feb6660a831d4', '2020-12-27 05:01:56', 0),
(307, 1, 'Smoothie', 7, 'no', 'Norway', 'Smoothie er perfekt for varme dager og inneholder ikke mye sukker.', '<p>Ha alt i en blender og miks sammen.</p>\r\n<p>Server i glass.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/7/1/2019', '307.jpg', '307-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-11', '18:42:40', 0, 5, 0, '', 270, '127.0.0.1\n167.114.64.97\n192.99.9.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.159.99', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'd6a18226e07b470c9125d42bbf1cbf59b564fc42', '2020-12-31 11:05:55', 0),
(308, 1, 'Svinekoteletter i stekeovn med wok chinese', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Svinekoteletter og wokblanding i ownen gj&oslash;r seg selv. Det tar litt tid &aring; steke svinekotelettene, men det er verd det.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Forvarm oven til 180 grader.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett inn svinekotelettene i en form inn i ovnen. De skal steke i 60 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&aring;r det er g&aring;tt 30 minutter setter du inn wok-blandingen i ovnen. Den skal steke i 30 minutter p&aring; 180 grader. Sett p&aring; vann til pastaen. Pastaen skal koke i 8-11 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Obs! Ikke spis fettet p&aring;svinekotelettene, det inneholder inzane mye d&aring;rlige kalorier.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '308.jpg', '308-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-12', '19:11:13', 0, 0, 0, '', 264, '167.114.64.97\n192.99.9.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n167.114.159.99', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '241f4c4d818500b4fefe3bb614c366ab7b4b71a8', '2020-12-27 05:04:57', 0),
(309, 1, 'Omelett med kyllingkj&oslash;ttp&oslash;lse', 1, 'no', 'Norway', 'En deilig frokost med omelett og kyllingkj&oslash;ttp&oslash;lser.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Visp sammen eggehvite og egg. Ha i en spiseskje vann pr egg. Kutt opp p&oslash;lsene i passende biter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stek p&oslash;lsene slik at de er gjennomstekt. Stek omeletten, n&aring;r den er gylden har du p&aring; pepper og legger p&oslash;lsebitene i.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Server med br&oslash;d, agurk, paprika og tomat.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/1/1/2019', '309.jpg', '309-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-14', '15:21:18', 0, 0, 0, '', 255, '127.0.0.1\n167.114.64.97\n192.99.9.25\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n167.114.158.241\n192.99.13.75\n167.114.159.99', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'e915c682796f772cc6bc9e6e4777b67c90f6e929', '2020-12-30 16:56:45', 0),
(310, 1, '&Oslash;rret, wokmiks og pasta', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En middag med mye proteiner.', '<p>Dagen f&oslash;r du skal lage denne retten tar du opp fisken og legger den i kj&oslash;leskapet.</p>\r\n<p>Sett ovnen p&aring; 200 grader. Finn frem en form hvor du har s&oslash;lvfolie i. Legg fileen i s&oslash;lvfolien. Lag en annen avdeling i samme formen hvor du har wokmiksen, eventuelt bruk en ekstra form. Fileen og wokmiksen skal steke i 30 minutter.</p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann og ha i pasta. Denne skal koke i 7-11 minutter, les pakningsveiledningen. </p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '310.jpg', '310-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-14', '19:05:08', 0, 0, 0, '', 253, '167.114.64.97\n173.249.30.147\n185.191.171.41\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n167.114.158.241\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n2607:5300:120:36c::1', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '7ed83d6b05ce8f5a208c5b75450e3ebd33cbd93d', '2020-12-27 05:07:47', 0),
(311, 1, 'Kyllingfilet, gr&oslash;nnsaker og ris', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En veldig god rett med mye gode proteiner.', '<p>Dagen f&oslash;r du skal lage denne retten m&aring; du ta opp to kyllingfileter fra fryseboksen og til kj&oslash;leskapet.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett ovnen p&aring; 200 grader. Finn frem s&oslash;lvfolie og legg det i en form. Ha i to kyllingfileter i formen. Disse skal bakes i 45 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; to kjeler med vann. En til ris og en til gr&oslash;nnsakene. Risen skal koke i 10 minutter, og gr&oslash;nnsakene skal bare ha et raskt oppkok.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '311.jpg', '311-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '15:50:01', 0, 0, 0, '', 163, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:14ed::2\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.159.99\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n167.114.116.38', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '0d6237a8b7b4fcf981e847e4741efc384265a9a6', '2020-12-25 16:00:20', 0),
(312, 1, 'Torsk, pasta og kuttede gr&oslash;nnsaker', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Man kan benytte ulike gr&oslash;nnsaker som tilbeh&oslash;r til torsk.', '<p>Ta ut torsken fra frysen dagen f&oslash;r du skal lage denne retten.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; ovnen p&aring; 200 grader. Legg fisken i en form dekket med aliminiumsfolie. Krydre med peppermix. Sett den inn i ovnen. Den skal steke i 30 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann til pasta og vann til gr&oslash;nnsakene. Kutt opp gr&oslash;nnsakene i passende biter. Kok alle gr&oslash;nnsakene utenom tomaten. Kok ogs&aring; pasta.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '312.jpg', '312-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '15:55:13', 0, 0, 0, '', 150, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.159.99\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n167.114.116.38', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '3d10b80e201223836fb311c3417117671ec5e578', '2020-12-25 16:00:52', 0),
(313, 1, 'Kylling, pommes frittes og brokkoli', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Hvis du velger riktig pommes frittes er denne retten veldig sunn.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\nSett p&aring; ovnen p&aring; 200 grader. Legg to kyllingfileter i en ildfast form med aliminiumsfolie. Krydre kyllingfiletene. Kyllingfileten skal steke i 45 minutter.</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Legg pommes frittes i en annen form. Stek de etter anvisningene p&aring; pakken.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 3</p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; en kaserolle med vann. Ha i brokkoli. Den skal ha et raskt oppkok, det vil si at den skal koke i ett minutt.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '313.jpg', '313-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '15:58:03', 0, 0, 0, '', 201, '185.191.171.42\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.158.241\n167.114.159.99\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n2607:5300:120:36c::1\n185.191.171.44', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '8e1c5e51c58a4496956fe5506789852f8e8e1276', '2020-12-26 16:26:24', 0),
(314, 1, 'Karbonadedeig spice mix, pasta og indisk wok', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En skikkelig klassikker kan man vel neppe kalle denne retten, men den er veldig sund.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 1</p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann til pastaen. Sett p&aring; pastaen s&aring; snart vannet koker. Pastaen skal koke i 9 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 2</p>\r\n<p>Stek 400 gram karbonadedeig. Tilsett en halv pose Spice Mix. Ta ut karbonadedeigen og legg den til side. Hvis du er kresen kan du legge aliminiumsfolie over karbonadedeigen for &aring; holde den ekstra varm.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Steg 3</p>\r\n<p>Stek wokblandingen i pannen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '314.jpg', '314-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:03:40', 0, 0, 0, '', 155, '2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.159.99\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '9a2b336d981c372f6fa80bc3f1509c3c5f5d1da6', '2020-12-26 11:20:16', 0),
(315, 1, 'Kyllingwok sweet chili med ris og gr&oslash;nnsaker', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En skikkelig god rett som er veldig sund.', '<p>Ta opp kyllingen fra frysen og legg den i kj&oslash;leskapet dagen f&oslash;r du skal tilberede den.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann til risen. Kutt opp kyllingen i passende biter p&aring; en hvit fj&oslash;l.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ta frem en ren kniv og en ny gr&oslash;nn fj&oslash;l hvor du kutter opp gr&oslash;nnsakene i biter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stek kyllingen. N&aring;r den er gjennomstekt tar du den ut av stekepannen og over p&aring; en talerken. Sett p&aring; risen hvis du ikke har gjort det enda. Stek s&aring; gr&oslash;nnsakene. N&aring;r gr&oslash;nnsakene er varme og gjennomstekte har du i woksausen og deretter kyllingen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '315.jpg', '315-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:09:34', 2, 0, 0, '', 352, '192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.159.99\n167.114.64.97\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n173.208.130.202\n192.99.4.163', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '2a7ac85142d16491df8b99223356219704f8698f', '2020-12-26 19:19:06', 0),
(316, 1, 'Taco med karbonadedeig', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Fredagsklassikeren med karbonadedeig.', '<p>lle har sin fredagstaco. Her er den jeg liker best &aring; lage, og alle ingrediense her er fra Coop Xtra.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Brun 400 g karbonadedeig. Tilsett spice mix og vann.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Del cherrytomatene i to. Skyll salaten. Legg de i ulike sk&aring;ler.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Server med vann med kullsyre.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '316.jpg', '316-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:16:06', 14, 0, 0, '', 259, '185.191.171.11\n192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.64.97\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'b486c2c4210e16740449e13f0be14169ebe086fb', '2020-12-26 22:54:52', 0),
(317, 1, 'Kyllingfilet, wok mix og pasta', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En enkel og smakfull rett er kylling bakt i ovnen med wok mix.', '<p>Ta opp kyllingfilet fra fryseren dagen f&oslash;r du skal lage retten. La den tine i kj&oslash;leskapet.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; ovnen p&aring; 200 grader. Lag to former av aliminiumsfolie i en ildfast form. I den ene formen har du kyllingfilet, krydret med pizzakrydder og peppermiks. I den andre formen har du de frosne wokgr&oslash;nnsakene.<br /><br />Sett alt inn i ovnen, det skal steke i 45 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Husk &aring; blande wokgr&oslash;nnsakene etter ca 25 minutter slik at de som har stekt minst kommer &oslash;verst. Hvis det samler seg vann i bunnen av wokgr&oslash;nnsakene pga de var frosne kan du helle det ut samtidig som du blander. <br /><br />Settt p&aring; vann til pasta.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Kok pastaen i 7-11 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '317.jpg', '317-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:23:34', 2, 0, 0, '', 230, '192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n2607:5300:60:3880::1\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.64.97\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n192.99.4.163', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'f69d0cd9acb521d80ee8d7b0b789ebd44ce67e9e', '2020-12-26 19:21:04', 0),
(318, 1, '4 skiver Superbr&oslash;d med b&oslash;ker&oslash;kt skinke, jalapenosost og skyr', 1, 'no', 'Norway', 'En sunn og god start p&aring; dagen.', '<p>Ta frem fire br&oslash;dskiver. Ha p&aring; skinke og ost. Server gjerne med paprika.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/1/1/2019', '318.jpg', '318-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:25:24', 0, 0, 0, '', 251, '167.114.64.97\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.159.99', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'ec67cbff1294f6aac0e20b4a38ea6a61626592fa', '2020-12-27 05:09:06', 0),
(319, 1, 'Surs&oslash;t saus med jasminris', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En slager er karbonadedeig, Uncle Bens surs&oslash;t saus og jasminris. Tar 15 minutter &aring; lage.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann til risen. Den skal koke i 10 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Brun en pakke med karbonadedeig. N&aring;r karbonadedeigen er brun tilsetter du sur s&oslash;t saus.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Server sur s&oslash;t saus og ris.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '319.jpg', '319-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:27:27', 2, 0, 0, '', 275, '2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n204.12.197.234\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2607:5300:60:3880::1\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'c30ef5d86555571bdf64b6aef73464c132622ee4', '2020-12-26 11:20:40', 0),
(320, 1, 'Fersk brokkoli', 6, 'no', 'Norway', 'Her er oppskrift p&aring; hvordan du kan koke fersk brokkoli.', '<p>Sett p&aring; vann til koking.<br /><br />Ta av plasten av brokkolien og skyll den godt i friskt vann. Kutt av stammen og kast den. Kutt brokkolien opp i passe biter ved &aring; f&oslash;lge stilkene. Kok brokkolien i 3-4 minutter. Den skal v&aelig;re knasende og spr&oslash;.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Brokkolien kommer fra Italia men vi dyrker den ogs&aring; i Norge. Den har jern, A- og B-vitamin, og har dobbelt s&aring; mye C-vitamin som appelsin i tillegg til at den er full av antioksidanter. Brokkoli b&oslash;r lagres kaldt, 0&ndash;2 grader celsius, og pakkes i plast.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/1/2019', '320.jpg', '320-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:29:42', 0, 0, 0, '', 251, '192.99.9.25\n2a01:4f8:161:81c1::2\n204.12.197.234\n173.249.30.147\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n5.9.108.254', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '37442460536e9734fd461a7aeb67f6ae446a36d3', '2020-12-26 19:21:38', 0),
(321, 1, 'Kyllingfilet med pasta og brokkoli', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En slager for den som trener og vil opp i muskelmasse, men ikke legge p&aring; seg.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ta ut kyllingfilet dagen f&oslash;r du skal steke den og la den tine i kj&oslash;leskapet. Sett p&aring; stekeovnen p&aring; 200 grader. Hvis komfyren din er treig kan du sette p&aring; to kjeler med vann, hvis ikke kan du gj&oslash;re de klar.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ha aliminiumsfolie i en form. Legg to stykk kyllingfileeter i formen. Krydre med pizzakrydder og peppermix. Hvis de er tint skal de steke i 40 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&aring;r det er 20 minutter igjen m&aring; du sette p&aring; vannet til pasta og gr&oslash;nnsakene. <strong>L</strong>a pastaen koke i 10 minutter, og la brokolien koke i 4 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '321.jpg', '321-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:31:03', 0, 0, 0, '', 259, '204.12.197.234\n173.249.30.147\n5.9.108.254\n167.114.158.241\n167.114.64.97\n144.91.125.96\n2a01:4f8:190:826b::2\n173.208.130.202', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'a98315d07101c432367f3f8ef63be7b9c69fcd3f', '2020-12-26 00:05:48', 0),
(322, 1, 'Karbonadedeig, fullkornpasta og FP pastasaus', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En klassiker som er sund s&aring; fremst man bytter kj&oslash;ttdeig med karbonadedeig.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\nSett p&aring; vann til pastaen. Kok pastaen s&aring; snart vannet koker. Pastaen skal koke i 9 minutter.</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hakk opp paprika. Du kan ogs&aring; ha i andre gr&oslash;nnsaker hvis du &oslash;nsker, f.eks. l&oslash;k.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Brun en pakke karbonadedeig. N&aring;r kj&oslash;ttdeigen er brun s&aring; tilsetter du paprika og pastasaus. La det putre i noen f&aring; minutter. Krydre med peppermix.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '322.jpg', '322-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:32:57', 9, 0, 0, '', 257, '173.249.30.147\n92.220.10.100\n5.9.108.254\n173.208.130.202\n95.91.110.121\n198.204.243.138', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '618de8f1f8114bd033cd9b4e6eae62c12380cc26', '2020-12-25 16:14:12', 0),
(323, 1, 'Wrap med philadelphia, laks og ruccola', 6, 'no', 'Norway', 'En klassiker i det spanske kj&oslash;kkenet.', '<p>Sm&oslash;r en tortilla med phillidelphia light. Ha p&aring; et stykke laks. Ha i litt ruccola. Rull det sammen til en wrap og del det i 5 stykker. Bruk en tannpirkel for &aring; holde wrappen p&aring; plass.<br /><br />Bueno vamos!</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/1/2019', '323.jpg', '323-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:38:02', 18, 0, 0, '', 248, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n167.114.64.97\n92.220.10.100\n5.9.108.254\n173.208.130.202\n95.91.110.121\n2a01:4f8:191:41f1::2\n167.114.211.237', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'f0fccd761faaed6eec7fa1892c3413e189e54014', '2020-12-27 05:09:38', 0),
(324, 1, 'Kyllingkj&oslash;ttdeig med spice mix, wokblanding og tortilla', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En rask middag.', '<p>Brun kj&oslash;ttdeig. Tilsett spice mix. Brun s&aring; wok miksen. Server med tortillas. </p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '324.jpg', '324-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:40:26', 0, 0, 0, '', 264, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2607:5300:60:3880::1\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.64.97\n92.220.10.100\n5.9.108.254', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '84e40a572af78154d16ca5cb8bb6fbd2f2f9cd0f', '2020-12-27 05:10:19', 0),
(325, 1, 'Gulrotkake', 5, 'no', 'Norway', 'Ved hjelp av Toro klarer alle &aring; bake denne kaken. Nettovekt er 396 g og servering er 87 g.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett ovnen p&aring; 210 g. Bland sammen kakemiks, vann, olje og gulrot. Ha i en form p&aring; 22-24 cm. La den steke i 35 min.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Glasuren lager du ved &aring; piske kremosten, mykt romtemperert sm&oslash;r. Tilsett s&aring; ostekrem miks. Ha det p&aring; kaken n&aring;r den er avkj&oslash;lt.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/5/1/2019/1_191116044610.png\" alt=\"https://summerslim.codecourses.eu/_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/5/1/2019/1_191116044610.png\" width=\"847\" height=\"847\" /></p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/5/1/2019', '325.jpg', '325-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:44:16', 0, 0, 0, '', 261, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n167.114.158.241\n167.114.64.97\n92.220.10.100\n5.9.108.254\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n173.208.130.202\n95.91.110.121', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '4143b242790fe0eca91c7e8454f02c4d3812f84d', '2020-12-25 16:19:42', 0),
(326, 1, 'Karbonadedeig, sur-s&oslash;t saus og basmatiris', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En rett med ingredienser fra det kinesiske kj&oslash;kkenet.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019/1_191116044912.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />Sett p&aring; vann til risen. Brun karbonadedeigen.<br /><br /><br /></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p><br /><br />Sett p&aring; vann til risen. Brun karbonadedeigen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ha risposen i vannet s&aring; snart det koker. Den skal koke i 12 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 4</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019/1_191116044935.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\" />N&aring;r karbonadedeigen er brun tilsetter du sur-s&oslash;t saus. Krydre den med peppermix.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '326.jpg', '326-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:48:04', 2, 0, 0, '', 236, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n95.91.110.121\n192.99.7.182\n2a01:4f8:191:41f1::2\n2a01:4f8:201:429a::2\n192.99.5.228', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', 'a6c609938ecffbc859dfcace1de9a1da225c6d37', '2020-12-25 16:20:05', 0),
(327, 1, 'Gresk yoghurth og havregryn', 1, 'no', 'Norway', 'Et sundt mellomm&aring;ltid.', '<p>Bland sammen en halv boks gresk yoghurth og havregryn.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/1/1/2019', '327.jpg', '327-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:52:38', 0, 0, 0, '', 236, '173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n173.208.130.202\n2a01:4f8:121:4076::2\n95.91.110.121\n192.99.15.199\n2a01:4f8:191:41f1::2', 0, '79.160.26.221', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', 'cc17559638efe8c2cf1987c5813f68ea9b1bfbb2', '2020-12-25 16:20:46', 0),
(328, 1, 'Meksikansk tomatsuppe med egg', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'En skikkelig god rett som passer i kalde h&oslash;stlige tider.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann til egg. Eggene skal koke i 9 minutter.<br />Sett ogs&aring; p&aring; vann til pasta. Pastaen skal koke i 11 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett p&aring; vann til suppen. Bruk 5 dl for en halv pose, 10 dl for en hel pose med suppe. R&oslash;r inn suppen og la det koke i 5 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img src=\"../_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019/1_191116045537.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '328.jpg', '328-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:54:18', 0, 0, 0, '', 116, '2a01:4f8:190:61af::2\n2a01:4f8:162:43c5::2\n207.180.218.247\n185.191.171.38\n2607:5300:60:3e58::1\n185.191.171.9\n185.191.171.45\n185.191.171.21\n185.191.171.22', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '7c9c6f0937e51e382f2ad2bcff42b0f874c4f5f4', '2020-12-14 23:07:17', 0),
(329, 1, 'Krydderkake med ostekrem', 5, 'no', 'Norway', 'Hvis du benytter Toros ferdigpakker lager du krydderkaken i en fei.', '<p><em><strong>Kaken:</strong></em></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett ovnen p&aring; 180 grader (varmluft 170 grader). Ta ut 50 g sm&oslash;r fra kj&oslash;leskapet og la det hvile ute slik at det blir romtemperert. Dette skal brukes til ostekremen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>R&oslash;r sammen 1 egg, 2dl vann og 100 g smeltet sm&oslash;r eller 1 dl flyttende margarin. Bland inn Toro-posens innhold (1 pose).</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hell r&oslash;ren i en smurt br&oslash;dform ca 1,5 liter og stek i midterste rille ca 35 minutter.<br />Eventuelt bruk en rundt form og stek i 30 minutter.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>La kaken avkj&oslash;le.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br /><em><strong>Ostekrem:</strong></em></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Pisk sammen 1 pk philadelpia light, 50 g mykt romtemperert sm&oslash;r. Tilsett s&aring; Toro Ostekrem og pisk til det blir en luftig krem (ca 5 minutter). Fordel over kaken.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Et kakestykke veier 85 g.</p>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/5/1/2019', '329.jpg', '329-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '16:56:59', 0, 0, 0, '', 251, '127.0.0.1\n173.249.30.147\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n2607:5300:60:3e85::1\n2a01:4f8:121:4076::2', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '5b16c60db2bd0d77e4932d23d280273075b1a19a', '2020-12-27 18:48:22', 0),
(330, 1, 'Gresk salat', 6, 'no', 'Norway', 'En gresk salat passer til mange retter som f.eks. grillmat og fisk.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Skyll salaten, la vannet renne av den. Ha den i en sk&aring;l.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Kutt cherrytomatene i to. Ha dem i salaten. TIlsett ogs&aring; oliven og fetaost.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/6/1/2019', '330.jpg', '330-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '17:03:04', 6, 0, 0, '', 138, '192.99.4.163\n2a01:4f8:162:30e2::2\n104.155.1.120\n185.191.171.11\n185.191.171.9\n185.191.171.38\n185.191.171.13', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '46f1c236ff072687e554b78da99d44ce0c763f4f', '2020-12-17 11:45:35', 0),
(331, 1, 'Torsk, pasta og gresk salat', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Gj&oslash;r som de i middelhavet og spis mager fisk med pasta og gresk salat.', '<p>Dagen f&oslash;r du skal servere denne retten m&aring; du ta opp torsken fra frysen og la den tine i kj&oslash;leskapet.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sett stekeovnen p&aring; 200 grader og sett p&aring; vann til pastaen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>Finn frem en form og ha i aliminiumsfolie. Legg torsken i formen og krydre. Sett den i stekeovnen. Den skal steke i 30 minutter p&aring; 200 grader.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Lag den greske salaten ved &aring; skyll salaten, la vannet renne av den. Ha den i en sk&aring;l. Kutt cherrytomatene i to. Ha dem i salaten. TIlsett ogs&aring; oliven og fetaost.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 4</strong></p>\r\n<p>N&aring;r det er 12 minutter igjen har du pastaen i det kokende vannet.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2019', '331.jpg', '331-thumb.jpg', '', '2019-11-16', '17:05:05', 6, 0, 0, '', 257, '127.0.0.1\n167.114.64.97\n207.180.224.141\n2a01:4f8:190:51c2::2\n178.151.245.174\n2a01:4f8:200:814b::2', 0, '79.160.26.221', 'E-mail not sent to administrators', 'de93c7dd5d4da5997384aad471608a927939bfa3', '2020-12-31 19:13:15', 0),
(332, 1, 'Chili con carne med karbonadedeig, b&oslash;nner og couscous', 2, 'no', 'Norway', 'Siden denne retten bruker karbonadedeig og b&oslash;nner er den sunn. Akuratt denne serveres med couscous.', '<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 1</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hakk opp l&oslash;k og paprika. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 2</strong></p>\r\n<p>M&aring;l opp couscous og sett p&aring; vann til den. Det skal v&aelig;re lite vann, s&aring; du m&aring; f&oslash;lge med koketiden. Ha i cous cous n&aring;r vannet koker. For en sunnere variant kan du bytte ut couscous med Uncle Bens Jasmin Boil-In-Bag, Uncle Bens Langkornet ris boil-in-bag eller Uncle Bens Fullkornsris Boil-in-bag.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Steg 3</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stek karbonadedeigen. N&aring;r den er brun tilsetter du b&oslash;nner, hakkede tomater, paprika og l&oslash;ken. Krydre med chilikrydder og spisskummen.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '_uploads/recipes/_image_uploads/2/1/2020', '332.jpg', '332-thumb.jpg', '', '2020-10-06', '21:07:14', 14, 0, 0, '', 33, '127.0.0.1\n167.114.158.215\n173.249.30.147\n144.76.14.153\n104.155.1.120\n173.249.2.13\n2a01:4f8:150:2370::2\n95.91.76.136\n107.150.59.98\n185.191.171.6', 0, '79.160.26.221', '', '09db026a5274cd3c8a1eb8de11b730bd8aca2546', '2020-12-27 18:48:18', 0)
")
